Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.78,0:00:15.24,Opening,,0,0,0,,My right hand holds a bowl of gold,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.24,0:00:19.79,Opening,,0,0,0,,And my left holds one of silver.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.79,0:00:24.46,Opening,,0,0,0,,Never one without the other,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.46,0:00:36.97,Opening,,0,0,0,,Two unseen bowls for each of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.97,0:00:45.98,Opening,,0,0,0,,The golden one is filled with joy,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.98,0:00:52.99,Opening,,0,0,0,,shining warmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.99,0:00:57.99,Opening,,0,0,0,,Since we met, my golden bowl
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.99,0:01:04.83,Opening,,0,0,0,,cannot hold all my happiness and love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.83,0:01:15.04,Opening,,0,0,0,,Golden joy, silver sadness,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.04,0:01:22.31,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would leave my past behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.31,0:01:27.12,Opening,,0,0,0,,For you, for the sake of love,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.12,0:01:34.06,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would empty the bowls of my past.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.79,0:01:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are, Misonoo-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.61,0:01:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Why on earth are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.43,0:01:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.48,0:02:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.43,0:02:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,4. The Music Box.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.74,0:02:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You are rather late.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.37,0:02:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you the party starts at noon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.11,0:02:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.84,0:02:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.04,0:02:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.70,0:02:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.11,0:02:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be seated, Misonoo-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.98,0:02:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.85,0:02:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But Miya-sama called yesterday. So why would...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.66,0:02:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I will ask you a few questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.93,0:02:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.01,0:02:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What are your hobbies? And what club will you join?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.93,0:02:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure! My hobbies...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.47,0:02:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I like baking!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.03,0:03:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But... I haven't decided which club to join...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.03,0:03:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I belong to the Flower Arranging Club and the Riding Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.62,0:03:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Flower Arranging?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.92,0:03:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I will join the Flower Arranging Club also!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.29,0:03:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,She smiled! Miya-sama smiled...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.30,0:03:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is your favorite author?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.63,0:03:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Good! She may not be upset anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.84,0:03:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Ex-Upery who wrote "The Little Prince" and Montgomery of "Ann of Green Gables"!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.31,0:03:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Little Prince"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.05,0:03:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And "Ann"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.43,0:03:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a little kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.40,0:03:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, they thought it was too childish! Well, let's see, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.10,0:03:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,De Sade! I also like De Sade!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.12,0:03:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The Marquis de Sade?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.33,0:03:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The Marquis de Sade? Of sadism and masochism?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.39,0:03:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonderful! Which one do you prefer?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.13,0:03:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.46,0:03:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Say sadism!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.53,0:03:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,She's perverted!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.44,0:03:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.42,0:04:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine. She is liberal...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.95,0:04:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all, Misonoo-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.62,0:04:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The results will be announced tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.63,0:04:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Failed. I have failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.66,0:04:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not final yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.16,0:04:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No... I'm sure. I couldn't even answer the questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.30,0:04:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not important at all! You did fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.84,0:04:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But... but it wasn't good that you were late.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.38,0:04:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened? I told you that being on time was so important!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.68,0:04:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But... yesterday Miya-sama called...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.79,0:04:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,She said that the party would start at three instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.94,0:05:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand. Why would she do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.07,0:05:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Did she really call? Are you sure it was Miya-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.74,0:05:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother answered...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.14,0:05:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It could have been anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.12,0:05:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.74,0:05:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Only she could do such a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.35,0:05:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Misaki Aya...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.30,0:05:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,After that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.84,0:05:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,How did I get home...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.17,0:05:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.73,0:05:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It could have been a Sunday like any other,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.05,0:05:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Spent baking a cake with Tomoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.74,0:05:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother... can this really be happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.92,0:06:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,A fake phone call... I can't comprehend such deception.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.86,0:06:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's really true, it's simply awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.07,0:06:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But... even worse, if I were in such a situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.27,0:06:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Could I be sure that I would not do the same...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.08,0:06:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako, it's Tomoko. She's at the corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.23,0:06:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured you might be back already...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.43,0:06:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,A fake phone call? What a cheat she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.90,0:06:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way to be sure, but Shinobu-san thinks it was her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.78,0:06:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.73,0:07:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Being admitted into the Sorority is a fabulous experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.38,0:07:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Something that any girl would want.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.26,0:07:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Even I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.53,0:07:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.53,0:07:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But I always knew I hadn't the slightest chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.33,0:07:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't believe I could be chosen either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.47,0:07:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,True...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.74,0:07:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's... that's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.45,0:07:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I don't have to worry about being slandered by anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.22,0:07:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.75,0:07:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What a relief!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.14,0:07:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been playing on these swings for so long...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.63,0:07:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.24,0:07:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We will be friends forever, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.24,0:07:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.31,0:07:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So anyway! Tomoko! The clubs!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.78,0:07:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So which will you join?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.80,0:08:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The Cooking Club, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.75,0:08:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll join too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.65,0:08:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't sure about the Flower Arranging Club...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.58,0:08:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get you an application form tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.56,0:08:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.68,0:08:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good morning, Shinobu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.81,0:08:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.88,0:08:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about "Passed"! And "Chosen"!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.82,0:08:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.53,0:08:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,As in "membership"!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.62,0:08:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.79,0:08:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, and the same to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.54,0:08:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean you haven't seen the announcement?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.30,0:08:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! It's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.10,0:09:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,There were nineteen candidates.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.94,0:09:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Every one them is superior to Misonoo-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.32,0:09:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You miserable potato heads!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.90,0:09:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.36,0:09:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Want me to say it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.92,0:09:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Potato heads!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.95,0:09:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still true what I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.00,0:09:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Go away! This is none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.20,0:09:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll not forget this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.54,0:09:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll protest directly to Miya-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.54,0:09:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't even attend the party!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.48,0:09:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Aha! How is it you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.81,0:09:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you how!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.31,0:09:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it was you who made the phony call, pretending to be Miya-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.62,0:09:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know anything about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.44,0:09:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's you that plays dirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.96,0:09:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That alone disqualifies you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.11,0:09:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'd never tolerate you as a member anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.44,0:10:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Well! Let's go, Misonoo-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.91,0:10:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.91,0:10:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.31,0:10:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Every year we have our arrogant lady, Miya-sama,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.92,0:10:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,...playing her games with the hearts of the freshmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.19,0:10:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.06,0:10:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.80,0:10:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well you don't really care, do you, Rei?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.20,0:10:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheer up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.61,0:10:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You were crying yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.55,0:10:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanted to join the Sorority, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.62,0:10:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but why me? It doesn't make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.89,0:11:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind all that. You made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.06,0:11:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy! And we're together, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.77,0:11:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.23,0:11:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.73,0:11:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoko, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.58,0:11:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.25,0:11:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So you made it after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.58,0:11:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.95,0:11:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't see the announcement, so this is news to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.46,0:11:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.08,0:11:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You look happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.29,0:11:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if I'm happy or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.41,0:11:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's your application to join the cooking club.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.47,0:11:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanted to join!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.18,0:11:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll probably join Flower Arranging after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.74,0:11:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like the rest of the Sorority members.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.60,0:11:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoko! Being a Sorority member doesn't mean I can't be your friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.42,0:11:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.49,0:12:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll meet you after school as usual! Tomoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.69,0:12:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.24,0:12:25.76,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,This island consists mostly of beaches, and is about three miles long.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.76,0:12:28.81,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,It is not more than a quarter of one mile wide.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.81,0:12:33.64,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,It has no tall trees. And near the eastern end, there is a fort.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.64,0:12:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok, very good. Be seated. Miss Misonoo, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.93,0:12:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.86,0:12:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.93,0:12:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,From the sixth line on, page twenty seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.56,0:12:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yessir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.10,0:12:50.17,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,Near the eastern end of this small island,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.17,0:12:54.14,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,Lebrand had built a hut, and lived with an old colored...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.14,0:12:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.13,0:12:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.55,0:13:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,A little louder please!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.09,0:13:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You jerks...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.87,0:13:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on, Misonoo-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.39,0:13:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yessir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.98,0:13:16.70,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,...and lived with an old colored man, Cora Jupiter,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.70,0:13:21.19,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,Lebrand was an eclectic man, and had unusual mental powers...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.04,0:13:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.07,0:13:26.51,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,...which greatly interested me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.51,0:13:32.09,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,His chief amusements were shipping, fishing...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.64,0:13:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.24,0:13:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.95,0:13:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.91,0:13:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.71,0:13:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.83,0:13:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.05,0:13:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... you... what is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.05,0:13:41.46,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,I can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.06,0:13:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.06,0:13:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.63,0:13:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.14,0:13:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.13,0:13:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.67,0:13:52.31,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Shut the hell up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.39,0:13:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit next to me if you can't hear!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.94,0:14:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear her perfectly!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.82,0:14:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up! You and you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.20,0:14:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, you! Stop this violence!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.30,0:14:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaoru-no-Kimi, you're so marvelous!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.10,0:14:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mix the sugar and egg white at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.11,0:14:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the key.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.51,0:14:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,First, you separate the egg white from the yolk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.18,0:14:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Please begin now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.13,0:14:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei, this is too much like a circus trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.99,0:14:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's easy for girls, but for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.14,0:15:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like you're implying that I'm not a girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.14,0:15:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me reasons to imply you are a girl, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.34,0:15:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok! Whatever it takes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.22,0:15:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I will do the eggs for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.19,0:15:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The key to resolving them into factors is to factor the common variables.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.70,0:15:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a key point.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.70,0:15:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, X minus forty-two times...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.44,0:15:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I can smell cookies...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.05,0:15:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be Nanako's cooking class.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.30,0:15:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoko! Being a Sorority member doesn't mean I can't be your friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.72,0:15:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.21,0:15:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.99,0:16:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wrong. It's not Nanako's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.47,0:16:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll apologize and make up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.40,0:16:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,To squeeze the tube, start from the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.49,0:16:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And make sure the cookie sheet is cooled off before you put it back in the oven.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.75,0:16:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You are doing quite well!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.68,0:16:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You are really good at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.09,0:16:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You're being a proper woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.02,0:16:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But you gave up womanhood!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.76,0:16:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so kind!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.56,0:16:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, Misonoo-san's womanhood...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.70,0:16:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,...should be especially good as far as cooking and selling is concerned!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.66,0:16:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What! Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.91,0:16:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Her womanhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.31,0:16:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.71,0:16:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Her mother used to work at an establishment near Jyoto University...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.51,0:16:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,...as a cocktail waitress!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.18,0:16:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Cocktail waitress?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.35,0:16:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,At a bar?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.82,0:16:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And at that bar she kept company with Professor Misonoo...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.19,0:17:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,...who already had both a wife and child.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.86,0:17:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,A wife and a child!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.25,0:17:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And then her mother kicked out his wife and the child!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.22,0:17:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Scandalous!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.54,0:17:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.74,0:17:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Are there really women like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.35,0:17:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell! Pornographer's daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.69,0:17:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! You daughter of a rat dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.61,0:17:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,My father is a lawyer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.86,0:17:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Greedy cheap private detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.82,0:17:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.76,0:17:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.86,0:17:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be true that my father had a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.37,0:17:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama and Papa met after he got divorced...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.59,0:17:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what my mom said.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.00,0:17:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,She... she wouldn't lie to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.52,0:18:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,There are times when you have to endure undeserved slander.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.13,0:18:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.40,0:18:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No one truly understands another...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.90,0:18:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,...but someone who cares can try to, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.36,0:18:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.66,0:18:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sign here, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.90,0:18:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,For Nanako?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.27,0:18:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,From whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.37,0:18:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Henmi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.57,0:18:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Henmi Takehiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.44,0:18:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.04,0:18:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.57,0:19:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.86,0:19:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope Tomoko is waiting for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.68,0:19:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Misonoo-san? Let's go home together...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.56,0:19:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.27,0:19:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But Tomoko is waiting for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.28,0:19:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.88,0:19:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.39,0:19:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoko? I saw her walking toward the music room...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.80,0:19:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.42,0:20:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't bother waiting for Nanako-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.43,0:20:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.59,0:20:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,She won't be able to go home with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.05,0:20:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,As a member of the Sorority, she has a lot of socializing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.99,0:20:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep in mind that she is no longer an ordinary student.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.46,0:20:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,She won't be able to go home together with you from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.33,0:20:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,From... from now on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.12,0:20:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,She asked me to tell you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.41,0:20:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to hear it from her directly!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.14,0:20:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.86,0:20:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Being her friend, can't you understand why she isn't here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.01,0:20:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So why the hell not?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.55,0:20:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako asked me to tell you because she didn't want to hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.16,0:20:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd not be so easily hurt if she told me herself!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.77,0:21:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.44,0:21:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell Nanako good-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.06,0:21:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoko didn't wait for me that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.54,0:21:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoko didn't forgive me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.54,0:21:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.34,0:21:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There is always tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.74,0:21:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And if not then, the day after...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.05,0:21:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We have been friends all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.43,0:22:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother... my dear brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.30,0:22:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to find out about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.90,0:22:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And also about my father, and my mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.57,0:22:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,...and if my father had a child...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.28,0:22:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,How can Takehiko know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.39,0:22:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,How long?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.53,0:22:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.06,0:22:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.54,0:22:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.41,0:22:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.55,0:22:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I was chosen as a Sorority member!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.68,0:22:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, congratulations! How wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.65,0:23:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Here is a package for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.26,0:23:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.89,0:24:14.10,Opening,,0,0,0,,I dreamed I was chasing a rainbow...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.10,0:24:19.57,Opening,,0,0,0,,Then the rainbow I was chasing was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.04,0:24:25.17,Opening,,0,0,0,,Before, I had no strength, no will.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.17,0:24:30.65,Opening,,0,0,0,,But now because of you, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.38,0:24:36.92,Opening,,0,0,0,,Feelings of love, like raindrops
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.92,0:24:42.39,Opening,,0,0,0,,Come pouring from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.39,0:24:45.13,Opening,,0,0,0,,This is surely a game
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.13,0:24:47.93,Opening,,0,0,0,,Of some mischievous fairy...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.93,0:24:50.33,Opening,,0,0,0,,Always dancing,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.33,0:24:55.60,Opening,,0,0,0,,Always capricious...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.28,0:25:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko's deception causes Tomoko to shun Nanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.35,0:25:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, at the Sorority initiation party, Nanako is shocked by Miya-sama's actions:
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.82,0:25:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Miya-sama deliberately drop a kenzan onto Saint-Juste's hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.63,0:25:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Next episode: Thorns of Doubt and Suspicion
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.03,0:25:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, Dear Brother... There is no end to my tears...
